  <brief_title>PTH - Preemptive Treatment for Herpesviridae</brief_title>
  <acronym>PTH</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy of a Preemptive Treatment by Ganciclovir or by Aciclovir in ICU Patients Requiring Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation and Presenting a Viral Replication (CMV and/or HSV) - Prospective, Randomized, Double-blinded Multicenter Trial</official_title>
