  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to show that a preemptive treatment by ganciclovir (for positive CMV
      viremia) or aciclovir (for positive HSV oro-pharyngeal PCR) is able to increase the number of
      ventilator-free days at Day 60.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
